=Description=

"We intend to create a hub of empowering circles for French-speaking change makers.  
Under multiple forms, we want to create holding spaces for cooperation and collaboration through mutual support and generative listening.
 
That will generate a Commonality of Cooperation as a physical and virtual place.  We want to take care of each other and train for collective action. We also want to share the existing corpus of the transition knowledge and skills, as well as those to come.
 
The hub intends to openly share with the actors of education and action-research, and  also with actors of Web-data, in order to contribute to the open data of transition."

